1. *Polje* je bilo prekriveno snegom. (The field was covered in snow.)
2. *Polju* je bila potrebna obnova. (The field needed to be renovated.)
3. *Polja* su puna cveća. (The fields are full of flowers.)
4. *Polju* je potrebna pažnja. (The field needs attention.)
5. *Poljem* je hodao kroz šumu. (He walked through the field in the forest.)
6. *Polja* su bila bogata. (The fields were rich.)